{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>庾恩利與內地網紅「碳酸」感情極好，社交平台上常看到兩人一起出遊，有時歐陽娜娜也會同行，近日他又釋出與碳酸聚餐的影片，而片中他拿著吸管喝女方嘴裡的飲料，似乎完全不怕對方口水，2人在鏡頭前笑鬧，互動十分親密。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126552438363394048719430.jpeg/GaUcrdmZc8zlzat490l2XNL-uskdEjIBG3evwxt3r8M\" alt=\"庾恩利與網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@sprinkle_my_tinkle）\"><figcaption>庾恩利與網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@sprinkle_my_tinkle）</figcaption></figure><p>更多庾恩利的相片：</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126552866555695104359764.jpeg/P0JISXhbhUCHRthGC1nZ3x1oYiKx4Z0u3ojzid6I84k\" alt=\"庾恩利（Instagram@sprinkle_my_tinkle）\"><figcaption>庾恩利（Instagram@sprinkle_my_tinkle）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126552869340844032405176.jpeg/OJE7ge7GxDWj_xkodQXDDVqJYKFajxN8I46pjiOOqY4\" alt=\"庾恩利（Instagram@sprinkle_my_tinkle）\"><figcaption>庾恩利（Instagram@sprinkle_my_tinkle）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126552872075661312504721.jpeg/lOddTOvMTq_ox0qFoxz9XQvAOojJrU1TOSV4RTkleEU\" alt=\"庾恩利（Instagram@sprinkle_my_tinkle）\"><figcaption>庾恩利（Instagram@sprinkle_my_tinkle）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126552874563014656056278.jpeg/NwdFvVlD0kTWobPUv03paZuwT7Jgjm3a-iCCSfoggkk\" alt=\"庾恩利（Instagram@sprinkle_my_tinkle）\"><figcaption>庾恩利（Instagram@sprinkle_my_tinkle）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126552876886790144068154.jpeg/UD8fOKWhcfZv7gBfx8cW_6QtcM1zYU8-waTSaMGk0mg\" alt=\"庾恩利（Instagram@sprinkle_my_tinkle）\"><figcaption>庾恩利（Instagram@sprinkle_my_tinkle）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126552864555012096014679.jpeg/jrHStPlEWIDJkBg9BkccIxUOAe3VfvdSwIf2AsCH9gI\" alt=\"庾恩利（Instagram@sprinkle_my_tinkle）\"><figcaption>庾恩利（Instagram@sprinkle_my_tinkle）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126552867013005312691824.jpeg/hVeScwI3_OG3xJnST39CFPJSeHmtlwYy_RBJEP0QSRA\" alt=\"庾恩利（Instagram@sprinkle_my_tinkle）\"><figcaption>庾恩利（Instagram@sprinkle_my_tinkle）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126552869739433984345816.jpeg/OridUEJU91SUgZom7W1VEnsCnByf1-9x6DwKF-g8Chc\" alt=\"庾恩利（Instagram@sprinkle_my_tinkle）\"><figcaption>庾恩利（Instagram@sprinkle_my_tinkle）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126552872696549376369581.jpeg/8gH3jZWHdS5hrF8OUSvc7zlW4LJiPsam6lFOeepRTnk\" alt=\"庾恩利（Instagram@sprinkle_my_tinkle）\"><figcaption>庾恩利（Instagram@sprinkle_my_tinkle）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126552875028713472230617.jpeg/epHORskHewnJ8qSPGgGkb_r98-jIS7oq6-zySuvs8ko\" alt=\"庾恩利（Instagram@sprinkle_my_tinkle）\"><figcaption>庾恩利（Instagram@sprinkle_my_tinkle）</figcaption></figure><p>沒想到畫面傳開後，被部分網友認為很噁心：</p><p>「就算是閨蜜也不會這樣吧，看到生理不適」</p><p>「不會覺得這就是自由吧？」</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126553019740065792674295.png/Z05FuTY1oWrB8R56I6cLtee11piAUdYJsnPgvbJz4L0\" alt=\"庾恩利用吸管喝網紅好友嘴裡飲料，挨轟非常不衛生。（微博圖片）\"><figcaption>庾恩利用吸管喝網紅好友嘴裡飲料，挨轟非常不衛生。（微博圖片）</figcaption></figure><p>更多網紅「碳酸」的相片：</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126553502584147968934562.jpeg/YCs8F9f0oLALR_Dm2qfIFILO0m_66AFZlVzre5Vc63s\" alt=\"網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）\"><figcaption>網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126553505033752576315082.jpeg/3Gcj7dkZmJqZ4biaA8kzNXOed_ok0g6Tju9Tno7vU54\" alt=\"網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）\"><figcaption>網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126553507231698944451927.jpeg/8u7iYfu_qtnEzeVOB_ckV9Gv0eLBjp4KWgSEWVoEhFk\" alt=\"網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）\"><figcaption>網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126553509601611776540396.jpeg/-ZRYTS2yY1yXbTKiZ5MPUjLJKmGi38ItK4Sw1yuEsNc\" alt=\"網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）\"><figcaption>網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126553511656951808530942.jpeg/d5nxCwFock9SUaugtcdMVs6f1S0G0I5NP6JGoz-iRqM\" alt=\"網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）\"><figcaption>網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126553501837561856357968.jpeg/4sTMEbhLS1D_kR-fcV77W-SoBe_8l033xzp3rsc6d64\" alt=\"網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）\"><figcaption>網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126553504417189888690532.jpeg/wJm5cbfaBKGeJg8uGVElgKX9l03JS1Xx735Uge9-VIE\" alt=\"網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）\"><figcaption>網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126553506774519808291043.jpeg/cMIBMeDsKjDAisbgYfPl4SFv-RYgh0QBOOy-zzjsvs8\" alt=\"網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）\"><figcaption>網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126553508989243392846912.jpeg/ZH5M4-HtvkhJ2BApbCfj52-YSngssnavJGKjKCRioyg\" alt=\"網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）\"><figcaption>網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126553511229132800942368.jpeg/iNWiZFPXQCO6E-rfyH9qLdIPX0DhPFeFjlsFaI5bBWg\" alt=\"網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）\"><figcaption>網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126553501502017536246018.jpeg/a0pq6G8dzBRCyCf2QS2KHOkhjMl1iVluT9R8G0_UfBs\" alt=\"網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）\"><figcaption>網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126553503850958848395418.jpeg/USdDrKc779E8V5ocO47X8KxslDB8JhdmC9mg7AvZoOw\" alt=\"網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）\"><figcaption>網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126553506090848256831470.jpeg/xnKKmEBsoXNw1UDFc49jck5cpPdAERagKskXaCrJF2g\" alt=\"網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）\"><figcaption>網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126553508532064256368210.jpeg/f6PQNMX05yAxtjaaz7e8O8kXzg4XTCC3Mi3CIjItwiI\" alt=\"網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）\"><figcaption>網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126553510830673920936725.jpeg/YI9cDlj0zSKYa9eVTbU4pM3QKobvnbg8S_6QREv-kEQ\" alt=\"網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）\"><figcaption>網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126553482753478656269417.jpeg/LfqrF2mAsjCQFyHwOiw-r_nMpm5P8OWFmEUj_ZhFI_0\" alt=\"網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）\"><figcaption>網紅「碳酸」（Instagram@tan__suan）</figcaption></figure><p>更痛批很不衛生等等，不過也有網友緩頰認為可能是假喝，或是就算是真喝，當事人不介意就好了，但輿論發酵沒多久，庾恩利似乎擔心節外生枝，迅速將影片刪除。</p><p>伊能靜回應該事件：</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126557172512067584607491.png/xGZHm8oUpGrBQVd_wms11nRSiSlNdcdaYhiMdmIYjHY\" alt=\"伊能靜回應兒子庾澄慶這次事件（微博@伊能靜）\"><figcaption>伊能靜回應兒子庾澄慶這次事件（微博@伊能靜）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126557174705819648280476.png/4Ps6mgg-ryHSkenWPO20lzvr9_U_XlPUpAjlnqQI5Z4\" alt=\"伊能靜回應兒子庾澄慶這次事件（微博@伊能靜）\"><figcaption>伊能靜回應兒子庾澄慶這次事件（微博@伊能靜）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126557177423859712263578.jpeg/XqIORrI0SSvFShJfg9xSz_7u4ErqXf7zPhOKSD4Tikg\" alt=\"伊能靜回應兒子庾澄慶這次事件（微博@伊能靜）\"><figcaption>伊能靜回應兒子庾澄慶這次事件（微博@伊能靜）</figcaption></figure><p>延伸閱讀：</p><p>女星兒「2度進加護病房」竟遭尪罵：母奶喝得不夠</p><p>【本文獲「TVBS新聞網」授權轉載。】</p></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-30T20:47:53.326716+00:00","quality":{"score":3,"chars":1244,"images":31,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}